      },
      "rationale": "Titanium alloy material properties (E, σ_y, E_t) were drawn from MMPDS-12 with lot-specific CoC verification. Screw geometry was measured by CMM on three production screws; mean dimensions used in the nominal model with ±1σ geometric uncertainty propagated via Monte Carlo sampling. Input uncertainty contribution to QoI variance was quantified and included in the validation metric E/uval calculation. Gradation 3 reflects systematic uncertainty quantification of model inputs."
    },
    {
