      "rationale": "Eleven non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs from a single production lot were split across two independent test laboratories (Lab A: N=6, Lab B: N=5). Certificate of conformance and dimensional inspection records confirm sample traceability. One-way ANOVA showed no statistically significant between-laboratory effect (p=0.31 for stiffness, p=0.44 for yield force), supporting pooling of results. Gradation 3 reflects multi-lab testing with statistical verification of laboratory equivalency."
