      },
      "rationale": "Testing followed ASTM F1717 protocol at a single static load condition. Only one test condition (compression-bending at 5 mm/min) was evaluated; torsion and tension-bending configurations were not included in this validation activity. This limits generalizability of the validation evidence to the compression-bending loading mode. Achieved Gradation 2 (below required Gradation 3) due to the single-condition limitation; offset rationale provided in the decision record."
